{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id77f59bc4-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s77zzz"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"77zzz"},"text":"§ 77zzz.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Effect on existing law","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Except as otherwise expressly provided, nothing in this subchapter shall affect (1) the jurisdiction of the Commission under the Securities Act of 1933 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s77a"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 77a","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] or the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s78a"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 78a","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] over any person, security, or contract, or (2) the rights, obligations, duties, or liabilities of any person under such acts; nor shall anything in this subchapter affect the jurisdiction of any other commission, board, agency, or officer of the United States or of any State or political subdivision of any State, over any person or security, insofar as such jurisdiction does not conflict with any provision of this subchapter or any rule, regulation, or order thereunder."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id77f59bc5-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1933-05-27/ch38"},"text":"May 27, 1933, ch. 38","children":[],"tail":", title III, § 326, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1939-08-03/ch411"},"text":"Aug. 3, 1939, ch. 411","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/53/1177"},"text":"53 Stat. 1177","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/tIX/s986/b/6"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203, title IX, § 986(b)(6)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-07-21"},"text":"July 21, 2010","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/124/1936"},"text":"124 Stat. 1936","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id77f59bc6-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id77f59bc7-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id77f59bc8-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Securities Act of 1933, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1933-05-27/ch38/tI"},"text":"act May 27, 1933, ch. 38, title I","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/48/74"},"text":"48 Stat. 74","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to subchapter I (§ 77a et seq.) of this chapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s77a"},"text":"section 77a of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Securities Exchange Act of 1934, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1934-06-06/ch404"},"text":"act June 6, 1934, ch. 404","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/48/881"},"text":"48 Stat. 881","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to chapter 2B (§ 78a et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s78a"},"text":"section 78a of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"